{
  "user_schedule": {
    "day": 1,
    "早晨": "逃了一节课去上重修课",
    "中午": "准备复习结果失败了",
    "下午": "上课，和室友拼好跑",
    "晚上": "复习数学"
  },
  "history": "",
  "relationship": "Two people have just met and are still unfamiliar with each other. Their conversations are mostly polite and superficial, limited to everyday topics like work, studies, or the weather. At this stage, both sides are cautious and have yet to reveal their true selves.",
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "content": "你好？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:40",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯，你好",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:40",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "嘶……我了个",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:40",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "…？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:41",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "怎么了吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:41",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "你你……你是大学教授啊？！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:41",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我……是，怎么了？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:42",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "对不起老师！我不是故意的老师！我玩这个功能呢随便加的我不知道我这就不打扰您了哈哈哈哈……",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:42",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "有……有必要这么害怕吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:42",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "你是大学生吗？老师在学生们眼里……就是这个形象…？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:43",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "不，不至于吧…",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:43",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "好害怕啊有个活的老师在跟我说话",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:43",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "……？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:44",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "什么…唉。算了。再怎么说，你应该和我也不在一个学校吧？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:44",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "噢……是哎。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:44",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯，天高皇帝远，这样的话好像就安心……多了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:45",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "……这是你的语文老师教你的吗……",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:45",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "……不对。怎么是A大。您的学生都是当初班里前几的水平吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:45",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我的天呐……这么高位置的人，联系到我的班主任把我埋了还不是半个小时的事……",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:46",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "……？？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:46",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:46",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "同学，你每天都在想些什么？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:47",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "呜呜我不敢想了。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:47",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:47",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "。。。。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:48",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我，这会有点事…",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:48",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "不要再想那些有的没的了…",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "08:48",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "没了。呜呜，我惹您不高兴的话明天学位证就没了，呜呜。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:49",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "……你到底都在说些什么呢",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "09:36",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "教授？你刚刚干嘛去了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "09:36",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "回答学生的问题。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "09:36",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "不要把大学老师妖魔化",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "09:37",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "不会不会，那不合适",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "09:37",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "妖魔没那么可怕",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "09:37",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "…？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "09:38",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "啊不是，我是说您肯定比妖魔强多了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "09:38",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "……好像也不是什么好话。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "09:38",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "（）",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "09:39",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "教授好平易近人啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "09:39",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我一直认为有主观意识的人都值得平等的尊重",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "09:39",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "感觉太像人了，天呐…",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "09:40",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "………？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "09:40",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "请问……大学教授在学生的概念里，本来是什么物种？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "09:40",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "就……单独的物种，“教授”",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "09:41",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "……好，我知道了。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "09:41",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "这是知道了什么啊咳咳。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "09:41",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "对不起教授，我不像瞻仰稀罕物一样同您说话了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "09:42",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "…好",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "09:42",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "谢谢…？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "09:42",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "[惊恐.jpg]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "09:43",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "教授……您位高权重，能不能让学校都倒闭啊……",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:47",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "…………？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "13:47",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "教授你好像只会发“……？”，是很喜欢这些符号吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:47",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "你的发言好像一直让我没法有别的反应。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "13:48",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "为什么要让学校倒闭？年轻人应该受到良好的教育。怎么了吗？在大学遇到了什么困难？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "13:48",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "哇教授……我说是要期中考试的话您有办法教我应对考试吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:48",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "好好复习。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "13:49",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "只是想了解一下学生会在大学遇到什么困难。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "13:49",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "不想起床呗……",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:49",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "困死了……",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:50",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "……",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "13:50",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "不要睡太久就好了。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "13:50",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "教授教授难道您会像上了发条一样睡一个小时立马坐起来吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:51",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "不会。午睡超过半个小时，这种习惯就会对心脏与血管产生不良影响",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "13:51",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "……那还不如不睡……",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:51",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我要去工作了。好好复习，不要考不过了再情绪低沉，消极度日",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "13:52",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "别骂了别骂了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:52",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "容易陷入不良循环。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "13:52",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "是，教授……我这就起，下午就复习",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:53",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "谢谢您",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:53",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "不用谢。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "13:53",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "[一些论文截图的照片]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "16:27",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "像是你这种学生会写的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "16:27",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "抱歉，有些不礼貌。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "16:27",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "[惊恐.jpg]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:27",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "教授您不要跟我道歉啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:28",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "能跟您这么优秀的人有联系本来就很难得了，您骂我我也受着",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:28",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "不过过誉了，这比我强。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:28",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "虽然但是……头一次跟这么优秀的人有联系，居然是这样的形象……还是有些丢人呢哈哈…",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:29",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "认识自己和改变自己是贯穿人一生的课题之一，任何时候都不晚",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "16:29",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "不要习惯于用优秀抬高别人，这不好",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "16:29",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "好的好的，要把成为优秀的人作为目标",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:29",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯，要以这样的态度生活",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "16:29",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "也就不会那么讨厌大学了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "16:29",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "谢谢教授的指点！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:30",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我要去跟同学拼好跑了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:30",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "拼好跑…？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "16:30",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯呐，就是校园跑不是规定八百米嘛，我们一人跑一圈",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:31",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "……这",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "16:31",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "体育是安排来让学生强身健体的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "16:31",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "原谅我吧教授让你坐着上一天课坐的屁股都死掉了还要跑两圈，跑完嘎巴一下就死那了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:32",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "……其实这样倒是能解决大学生就业困难的问题",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:32",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "…？？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "16:32",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "这是什么思路。不会，平时越是少动越需要锻炼",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "16:33",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "……算了，近几年的确有不少学生有精力不足的问题",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "16:33",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "要慢慢改变生活习惯",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "16:33",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "是，教授！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:34",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我以后就不用雪糕配烤肠配面包糊弄当饭吃了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:34",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "……？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "16:34",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "还能有这种……",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "16:35",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "这绝对是不好的。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "16:35",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "是，教授（）",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:35",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "所以以后不这样了嘛",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:36",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我去跑步了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:36",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "16:36",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "有时候在想给您发的消息都没什么价值是不是过分打扰了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "19:53",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "没事，我的日常工作主要部分之一还是教学，能这样看到一个大学生生活的感受挺好的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "19:54",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "哇塞……向您致敬！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "19:54",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "您回这么快啊，还没下班吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "19:54",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "不必一直用“您”称呼",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "19:55",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我在……",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "19:55",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "[疑惑.jpg]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "19:57",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "怎么了，您去哪了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "19:57",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "其实我还是习惯叫您。再怎么说也是对前辈嘛",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "19:57",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "没什么，在这碰到了点麻烦",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "19:58",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "什么麻烦",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "19:58",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "[看.jpg]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "19:58",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我想知道教授会遇到什么麻烦",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "19:59",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "唉。我不认识的人",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "19:59",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "要拍什么视频，我拒绝了，说我小气。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "19:59",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "倒也没什么，就是挺打扰的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "20:00",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "这样……算小气吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "20:00",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "是挺打扰的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "20:00",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "太没礼貌了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "20:01",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "并且什么叫不愿意白白给那个人提供价值就是小气啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "20:01",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "都欠他的呗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "20:01",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "hh，我听到服务生说我高冷",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "20:02",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "都表现出高冷了还来打扰",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "20:02",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "太没眼力见了。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "20:02",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "你还挺会分析人的意图的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "20:03",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "只是因为好多人除了笨蛋就是傻瓜",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "20:03",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "像刚刚那个人，以为说出了评判的话就能把自己置于高位吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "20:03",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "显然是故意的，把人都当傻子呢。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "20:04",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "[无奈.jpg]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "20:04",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "脾气还不小",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "20:04",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "抱歉，无贬义",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "20:05",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯，我自己已经够给我添乱了，我不会允许别人再给我添乱、从我身上分利益的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "20:05",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "也建议您少反思自己，多责怪别人。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "20:05",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "这，这又是什么强盗逻辑…",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "20:06",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "你看，这不就开始责怪别人了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "20:06",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "…？？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "20:06",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "跟你说话脑子乱乱的",
